.Dd $Mdocdate: July 16 2013 $
.Dt HT 4 macppc
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ht
.Nd HyperTransport bus
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "ht* at mainbus0"
.Cd "pci* at ht?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the HyperTransport bus found on Apple
.Tn G5
machines.
The HyperTransport bus is functionally very similar to the
.Xr pci 4
bus.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr pci 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 3.9 .
